title: DataCore SANsymphony: Alerts
agents: datacore_rest
catalog: storage/datacore
license: GPLv2
distribution: andre_eckstein
description:
 This check monitors alerts reported by a DataCore SANsymphony storage system.
 It displays the total number of alerts and categorizes them by severity level
 ({info}, {warning}, {error}, {trace}).

 The check returns {CRIT} if any error-level alerts are present,
 {WARN} if warning-level alerts exist, and {OK} otherwise.

 This check requires the special agent configurable through
 "DataCore SANsymphony via REST API".

discovery:
 One service is created for the SANsymphony system.
